 YouTube总浏览量突破10亿的英语VTuber“Filian”是谁？积极开展基于VRChat的活动https://www.moguravr.com/vtuber-filian/井文 Fri, 12 Apr 2024 09:01:15 +0000 VTuberFilian https://www.moguravr.com/?p=249664 <p>活跃于英语国家的VTuber“Filian”备受关注。 Filian 是一名 VTuber，于 2021 年出道，主要活跃在 YouTube 和 Twitch 上。在撰写本文时，YouTube 订阅者数量为 25 [...]</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/vtuber-filian/">YouTube总浏览量突破10亿的英语VTuber“Filian”是谁？活跃于 VRChat，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p>活跃于英语国家的VTuber“ <a href="https://www.twitch.tv/filian" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Filian</a> ”备受关注。 Filian 是一名 VTuber，于 2021 年出道，主要活跃在 YouTube 和 Twitch 上。截至撰写本文时，YouTube 订阅者数量已超过 250 万。</p><p>到目前为止，在日本的认可度还没有那么高，但从2024年开始，它的受欢迎程度逐渐上升。被人津津乐道的菲利安先生到底是谁？在这篇文章中，我们将介绍它从“开始”到现在的进展。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.kntqml3z272o-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.kntqml3z272o-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.kntqml3z272o-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.kntqml3z272o-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.kntqml3z272o-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.kntqml3z272o-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.kntqml3z272o-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> （ <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://thevtuberawards.com/&amp;sa=D&amp;source=docs&amp;ust=1712913605508161&amp;usg=AOvVaw0-Y7qwgD7d7P55C3FRcagr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">引自2023 Vtuber Awards</a> ）</p><h2>使用 VRChat 的活动目前正在进行中</h2><p>Filian是一位基于社交VR“VRChat”的VTuber。各种项目正在进行中，例如在 VRChat 游戏世界中玩耍、与其他玩家互动、制作一次性视频给粉丝带来惊喜。其特点是飞行、跳跃等，用全身积极活动，外形可爱。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="专业人士讲解 VRC 物理" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SEVJCulO0nw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="如果我大便，视频就会结束" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kxgbtpUjPXA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p></p><p></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-1024x542.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-1024x542.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-300x159.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-768x407.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-1536x813.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ugiw0pj99va1-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="542" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ivi6abm8rquz-jpg.webp"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-249661" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ivi6abm8rquz-jpg.webp" alt="" width="1600" height="768" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ivi6abm8rquz-jpg.webp 1600w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ivi6abm8rquz-300x144.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ivi6abm8rquz-1024x492.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ivi6abm8rquz-768x369.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.ivi6abm8rquz-1536x737.webp 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.7d8ud45okb71-jpg.webp"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-249662" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.7d8ud45okb71-jpg.webp" alt="" width="1600" height="844" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.7d8ud45okb71-jpg.webp 1600w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.7d8ud45okb71-300x158.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.7d8ud45okb71-1024x540.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.7d8ud45okb71-768x405.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/cc0819e1c41d56bb8c425077c73d8646-kix.7d8ud45okb71-1536x810.webp 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /></a></p><p> VTuber的“3D头像”使用了创作者Jingo和Komado创建的3D模型。另一个特点是，许多广播（视频）都使用全身跟踪设备。我们还在 VRChat 之外使用 3D 头像，包括在反应视频和游戏评论中。</p><p>自 2021 年开始活动以来，Filian 的人气稳步上升，并于 10 月与 Twitch 签署了合作伙伴协议。同年11月，Twitch订阅人数达到1万。第一个视频于 2021 年 11 月发布在 YouTube 上。大约四个月后，即2022年3月，注册用户数突破10万。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Filian 在 Huggy&#39;s 玩了 5 个晚上 [Poppy Playtime]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/he7rwbXV67k?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe><br /> （Filian 的 YouTube 频道上最古老的视频。其中涉及玩 FNAF 模仿游戏“Huggy 的五夜”）</p><h2>公益活动8小时不间断直播</h2><p>此后人气和知名度持续上升，并于 2022 年 5 月宣布将转为全职主播。随后，9 月份，YouTube 订阅者数量突破 100 万。</p><p>大约从这个时候开始，菲利安开始进一步扩大他的活动，并在2023年初，他进行了一场慈善广播，旨在为心脏病研究筹集资金。本次直播持续约8小时，内容包括在“VRChat”上的高尔夫游戏世界“Putt Putt Pond”打球、让Filian先生跑步（VR）等活动。当时的分发活动引起了广泛关注，最终捐款总额达到约5万美元（750万日元）。</p><p> 2023年3月，他宣布将加入内容创作机构<a href="https://www.mythictalent.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mythic Talent</a> 。该机构拥有 VTuber、主播和前职业游戏玩家等成员，截至 2024 年，仅 VTuber 就有 34 名。此外，他还担任12月举办的海外在线VTuber活动“ <a href="https://thevtuberawards.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vtuber Awards 2023</a> ”的主持人。我负责在各个​​部门引入VTuber。 2024年2月，宣布限时出演赛车游戏《 <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2598980/Oh_Baby_Kart/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Oh Baby Kart</a> 》。你可以看到Filian和他合作的VTuber们在比赛中玩得很开心。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="FILIAN 被添加到游戏中" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2qNvmRNpoGE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h2>作为个人VTuber频道取得了巨大的成就</h2><p>2024年3月8日，Filian YouTube频道总浏览量突破10亿。一些VTuber频道（团体类型）已经达到了这一观看次数，但Filian是第一个实现这一目标的个人VTuber频道。</p><p>菲利安先生开始在日本引起关注。 2024年他会取得怎样的成功和突破？我很期待观看它。</p><p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@filianIsLost" target="_blank" rel="noopener">点击此处</a>查看 Filian 的官方 YouTube 频道</p><p><a href="https://www.twitch.tv/filian/videos?filter=archives&amp;sort=time" target="_blank" rel="noopener">单击此处</a>查看 Filian 的官方 Twitch 频道</p><p>作词：伊布米</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/vtuber-filian/">YouTube总浏览量突破10亿的英语VTuber“Filian”是谁？活跃于 VRChat，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; 
