。</p><p>点击<a href="https://collection.rakuten.co.jp/feature/j1_nijisanji_2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>查看特别合作网站。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000865.000030865.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ANYCOLOR Co., Ltd. 新闻稿</a></p><h2>“深町俊成的V-Bara！！！”决定与Holostars 5周年纪念演唱会合作</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/0d003debcb0d6a3cb0835141e04fd2d4-kix.cbnwrqkkmgem-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/0d003debcb0d6a3cb0835141e04fd2d4-kix.cbnwrqkkmgem-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/0d003debcb0d6a3cb0835141e04fd2d4-kix.cbnwrqkkmgem-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/0d003debcb0d6a3cb0835141e04fd2d4-kix.cbnwrqkkmgem-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/0d003debcb0d6a3cb0835141e04fd2d4-kix.cbnwrqkkmgem-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/0d003debcb0d6a3cb0835141e04fd2d4-kix.cbnwrqkkmgem-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/0d003debcb0d6a3cb0835141e04fd2d4-kix.cbnwrqkkmgem-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> Niconico Channel+正在播出的《深町利成的V Bara!!!》和Hololstars 5周年纪念演唱会已确定合作。</p><p>作为第一个合作项目，“即将在5周年纪念现场！Holo Star Call SP！”将于5月28日（星期二）20:00在“深町俊成的V Bara！！！”中播出。</p><p>此外，深町久成也将参加 Holostars 5 周年纪念现场。渗透过程将于六月进行现场直播。</p><p> <a href="https://nicochannel.jp/fvvara/live/smLmKmxi62nEHhN944gpFs9a" target="_blank" rel="noopener">点击此处</a>查看第一个合作项目的广播页面。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000014538.000007006.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">角川株式会社新闻稿</a></p><h2>“虹山寺文具”商品销售</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/0d003debcb0d6a3cb0835141e04fd2d4-kix.rmda0htr8r3f-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/0d003debcb0d6